settings.description: Just a simple traditional level with note blocks, try to find all 5 e-Coins!
A remake of Super Mario World 1-3. The rotating chain platforms aren't in SMB3, so several SMB1 Platforms have been added to help you collect coins.
Mario explores a dense world and was trapped by some ghosts from a very haunted mansion, in which he falls from the bottom and Mairo tries to climb to the top to find his most beloved home

Remake of the first Switch Palace in Super Mario World.
The Bonus Room Checkered Floors/Ceilings are glitched when they are longer than 15 tiles so I had to separate them with Unbreakable SMB1 Blocks.
SMB1's 4-1, only existing so you can move on to the one with the warp zone in it.
